      <title>美联储降息将成为亚洲各国央行的发令枪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/fed-cut-to-serve-as-starting-gun-for-central-banks-across-asia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经历了两年多的货币困境后，美联储周三将降息四分之一个百分点，亚洲各国央行终于松了一口气。不过，该地区货币政策的未来之路仍将坎坷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/fed-cut-to-serve-as-starting-gun-for-central-banks-across-asia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
