    <item>
      <title>中东紧张局势和库存成为焦点，油价企稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-18</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员评估中东紧张局势加剧、美国库存增加迹象以及美联储可能的利率路径，油价在连续两天上涨后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-18</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 23:27:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚央行将重点关注批发数字货币而非零售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/australia-to-focus-on-wholesale-rather-than-retail-case-for-cbdc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚储备银行表示，考虑到零售版本可能带来的适度收益和潜在的复杂性，它将专注于批发央行数字货币的可能用例。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/australia-to-focus-on-wholesale-rather-than-retail-case-for-cbdc</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 23:20:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bausch Health 聘请 Jefferies 进行债务再融资，帮助分拆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/bausch-health-taps-jefferies-to-refinance-debt-aid-spinoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，博士伦医疗公司 (Bausch Health Cos.) 正在与杰富瑞金融集团 (Jefferies Financial Group) 合作，探讨对部分债务进行再融资，以助力其长期计划的剥离眼保健公司博士伦 (Bausch + Lomb) 的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/bausch-health-taps-jefferies-to-refinance-debt-aid-spinoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 22:40:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
