    <item>
      <title>Point72 的 Drossos 表示，美联储降息将导致美元走弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/fed-cuts-will-usher-in-weaker-dollar-era-point72-s-drossos-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Point72 Asset Management 策略师兼经济学家索菲亚·德罗索斯表示，随着美联储开始降低借贷成本且世界其他地区出现乐观迹象，美元正进入下行趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/fed-cuts-will-usher-in-weaker-dollar-era-point72-s-drossos-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 21:33:04 GMT</pubDate>
